Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean this is your world right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you guys actually don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We did not know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Nothing other than the mud whale... Nothing.
