Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}So many friends and fellows died...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all buried by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be this calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why did so many people have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray, for the people who I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Waa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.13,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(796,1000)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lykos{\i0} is not my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.59,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1366,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the name of this creature called {\i1}nous{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.13,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,1000)}Νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nous,{\i0} means the shape of soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is a creature that absorbs emotions from human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.78,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,1000)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,feeding Lykos with our feelings as its nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have flat minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:17.08,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,People who discovered the {\i1}nous{\i0} decided to deposit their emotions with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz emotions will destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world outside, where you want to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.60,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1256,1000)}απάθεια
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,people without emotions command the {\i1}apatheia{\i0} with no heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight in an endless war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there particularly anything you want from our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back, and leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die on this ship by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if there's a war or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to escape from the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to give all my feelings to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Oni! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}There are hundreds, thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}no, numbers of {\i1}minds{\i0} passing by and disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Oh my, I know this chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.78,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\bord2\pos(1036,1000)}hypergraphia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}When I can't stop writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I see this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Benihi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad for it, but I don't want to get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly know what you did right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro? Hey Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Sami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw a lot of gravestones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really the only things you have seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe what you two said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taisha, tell everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,traveling to that island is strictly prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the procurement of goods is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Canceled, you can't even take a needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool your head a bit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So Oni, you were OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart wasn't taken by that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw strange stuffs at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe, it's an creature that can truly absorb your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it for a split second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The war of the outside world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.44,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,1000)}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is a war using {\i1}thymia,{\i0} I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl must be able of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni, I'd leave it far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you thing the graves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I start to be scared about the world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why didn't you help me at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If Lycos didn't give me a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That's why we have flat minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did she help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finishing my meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guy who saw you were forced to go with Oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really forced to go, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lucky, you get released at a good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Around the mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}there are large grasshoppers called {\i1}star locust{\i0} living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}They live on eating wastes from the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}They metamorphose into a structure suitable for long range movement
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}when their population grows to a certain number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}They start emitting lights and moving far away at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We call it a {\i1}locust phenomenon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take a good place before it gets dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami, Nezu, Lo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,wait a moment please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still suffering from the injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Neli, I am taking care of the presbyters at this tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just a {\i1}Muin,{\i0} but please don't hesitate to ask me if you need any assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the presbyters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I need that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.48,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1148,1000)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me back to {\i1}Lykos{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take my minds away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is normal to have minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You will soon get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take Lykos out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get sent to the {\i1}internal{\i0} again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the locust with her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a deal, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli you should take a good place as soon as possible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you alone even if you don't have minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You made so many graves for your fellows, all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never leave such a good girl alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? With Lykos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl from that island? Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Hi, call me Nezu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If she is found, then it's much more than not being able to see the locust.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By taking my anti sand cloak this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,she will never be recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How you dare renting your dirty cloak to a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,without even have it washed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But then how can I hide you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are spaces on the top of the 4th tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few more steps to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,lift me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You lifted my up last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}Last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The previous locust phenomenon is three years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}Lift me up! I can't walk anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are getting heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami is not heavy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro's spiteful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you can walk yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I carry you on my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we're yet to see Mr. Grassho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few steps left, keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost my child in an accident by the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then I love every small child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Kuchiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold my hand too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So..Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Still yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Grassho? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I entered the military academy when I was 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I headed to the dormitory with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the day I parted from my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But for us, whose emotions have been taken away, we didn't even have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to the dorm was long and steep, and my luggage was heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be a good soldier with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your memory inside that creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not even troubling with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why it becomes so painful to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you do have your heart in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The same!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe the mud whale
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,will get to where your family live some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Also you will never be a soldier here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never die in a fight here in the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos, let's stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something important to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.72,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fallaina{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where are they going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanna go somewhere far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}July 8, 93 S.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We recognized a locust phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The crowd was flying above the mud whale with lights emitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And they leaved for somewhere far away in the sea of sand by the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up now, take your breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit, you dumb-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand teaming with you any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Troubling me all the time, you destroyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since our parents died,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we started to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been looking after your younger brother and sister, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We are helping each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, you're sprinkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been looked after, haven't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call it helping each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading the farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, my bro's full of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't work as fast as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I started earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My bro is good at everything except for physical fitness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sow together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The locust yesterday is really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Lykos after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent her back to the central tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I brought her out secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami, Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,do me a favor please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have works to do at the presbytery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So.. sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos said she has something to tell the presbyters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the presbytery refused to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And in fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The presbytery has sent the vigilante group out behind Taisha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that they are alerting the surrounding sea areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She is guarded and nobody is allowed to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I've never heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Let me talk to the representative of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something important that I must tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taisha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally threw away Chakuro's records.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let others do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy said he want to know the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so he keeps the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the same feeling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The presbytery is hiding the girl of the adrift island from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The presbytery is conventionally controlling over the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every "Muin" can become the presbyter when over 61 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they'll be informed with the history of mud whale
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the relations between the world and the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief doesn't have any political power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only required to be a symbol being loved by the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 19 years before I can enter the presbytery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I'm just a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep playing as a well-made idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It isn't that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care Taisha-sama is a puppet or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I always support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for the sake of mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try to be a good puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.02,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,1000)}σκύλος
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Skulax here, starting the operation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape from here, as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:22.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fallaina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, is that a sand dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.44,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1038,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sinners of the whale,{\i0} are targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sinners?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}My records as the official record clerk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ended this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The record about the mud whale, in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}will be my personal
